<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>StudyGateItaly — Your Gateway to Studying in Italy</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;1,400&family=Fraunces:wght@700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
:root{
  --g:#009246;--g2:#006830;--r:#CE2B37;--w:#fff;
  --bg:#f7f8f5;--dark:#0f1a12;--text:#1c2b1e;--muted:#5a6e5c;
  --card:#ffffff;--border:#e2e8e3;
  --shadow:0 2px 16px rgba(0,80,30,0.08);
}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
body{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);line-height:1.6}

/* LANG SWITCHER */
.lang-btn{display:none}
[lang="ar"] .ar{display:block!important}
[lang="ar"] .en{display:none!important}
[lang="en"] .ar{display:none!important}
[lang="en"] .en{display:block!important}
.ar{display:none}

/* NAV */
nav{
  background:rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
  backdrop-filter:blur(12px);
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
  padding:0 2rem;height:64px;
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;
  position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100;
}
.logo{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:1.4rem;color:var(--dark);text-decoration:none;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}
.logo em{color:var(--g);font-style:normal}
.nav-right{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1.5rem}
.nav-links{display:flex;gap:1.2rem;list-style:none}
.nav-links a{text-decoration:none;color:var(--muted);font-size:0.875rem;font-weight:500;transition:color 0.2s}
.nav-links a:hover{color:var(--g)}
.lang-toggle{
  background:var(--dark);color:white;
  border:none;padding:6px 14px;border-radius:20px;
  font-size:0.8rem;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;
  font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;
}
.cta-nav{
  background:var(--g);color:white;
  padding:8px 18px;border-radius:8px;
  text-decoration:none;font-size:0.875rem;font-weight:600;
  transition:background 0.2s;
}
.cta-nav:hover{background:var(--g2)}

/* HERO */
.hero{
  min-height:90vh;
  display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
  align-items:center;gap:3rem;
  padding:4rem 4rem;
  max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;
}
.hero-text h1{
  font-family:'Fraunces',serif;
  font-size:clamp(2.5rem,5vw,4rem);
  line-height:1.1;
  color:var(--dark);
  margin-bottom:1.5rem;
}
.hero-text h1 span{color:var(--g)}
.hero-text p{font-size:1.1rem;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:2rem;max-width:480px}
.hero-btns{display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap}
.btn-primary{
  background:var(--g);color:white;
  padding:14px 28px;border-radius:10px;
  text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;font-size:1rem;
  transition:all 0.2s;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;
}
.btn-primary:hover{background:var(--g2);transform:translateY(-1px)}
.btn-secondary{
  background:transparent;color:var(--dark);
  padding:14px 28px;border-radius:10px;
  text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;font-size:1rem;
  border:2px solid var(--border);transition:all 0.2s;
}
.btn-secondary:hover{border-color:var(--g);color:var(--g)}
.hero-image{position:relative}
.hero-image img{
  width:100%;border-radius:24px;
  object-fit:cover;height:500px;
  box-shadow:0 24px 64px rgba(0,80,30,0.15);
}
.hero-badge{
  position:absolute;bottom:-20px;left:-20px;
  background:white;border-radius:16px;
  padding:16px 20px;box-shadow:var(--shadow);
  border:1px solid var(--border);
}
.hero-badge .number{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:1.8rem;color:var(--g);font-weight:900}
.hero-badge .label{font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--muted);margin-top:2px}

/* STATS BAR */
.stats-bar{
  background:var(--dark);
  padding:2rem 4rem;
  display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);
  gap:2rem;text-align:center;
}
.stat .n{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:2rem;color:white;font-weight:900}
.stat .l{font-size:0.8rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);margin-top:4px}

/* SECTIONS */
.section{padding:5rem 4rem;max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto}
.section-full{padding:5rem 4rem;background:white}
.section-full-inner{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto}
.eyebrow{font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--g);margin-bottom:0.75rem}
.section-title{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:clamp(1.8rem,3vw,2.5rem);color:var(--dark);margin-bottom:0.75rem;line-height:1.2}
.section-sub{color:var(--muted);font-size:1rem;margin-bottom:3rem;max-width:600px}

/* GUIDES GRID */
.guides-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(300px,1fr));gap:1.5rem}
.guide-card{
  background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius:16px;padding:1.8rem;
  transition:all 0.2s;cursor:pointer;text-decoration:none;color:inherit;display:block;
}
.guide-card:hover{border-color:var(--g);box-shadow:var(--shadow);transform:translateY(-2px)}
.guide-icon{font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:1rem}
.guide-card h3{font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:0.5rem;color:var(--dark)}
.guide-card p{font-size:0.875rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6}
.guide-tag{
  display:inline-block;margin-top:1rem;
  font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:600;
  color:var(--g);background:#f0fff4;
  padding:4px 10px;border-radius:20px;
}

/* STEPS */
.steps-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(180px,1fr));gap:1rem;position:relative}
.step-card{
  background:var(--bg);border-radius:16px;
  padding:1.5rem;text-align:center;
  border:1px solid var(--border);
}
.step-num{
  width:44px;height:44px;background:var(--g);color:white;
  border-radius:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  font-weight:700;font-size:1rem;margin:0 auto 1rem;
  font-family:'Fraunces',serif;
}
.step-card h3{font-size:0.9rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:0.4rem;color:var(--dark)}
.step-card p{font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.5}

/* SERVICES */
.services-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(280px,1fr));gap:1.5rem}
.service-card{
  border-radius:16px;padding:2rem;
  border:2px solid var(--border);
  transition:all 0.2s;position:relative;overflow:hidden;
}
.service-card.featured{border-color:var(--g);background:#f0fff4}
.service-badge{
  position:absolute;top:16px;right:16px;
  background:var(--g);color:white;
  font-size:0.7rem;font-weight:700;
  padding:4px 10px;border-radius:20px;
}
.service-price{
  font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:2.5rem;
  font-weight:900;color:var(--dark);
}
.service-price span{font-size:1rem;font-weight:400;color:var(--muted)}
.service-card h3{font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:600;margin:0.5rem 0;color:var(--dark)}
.service-card p{font-size:0.875rem;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:1rem;line-height:1.6}
.service-features{list-style:none;margin-bottom:1.5rem}
.service-features li{font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--muted);padding:4px 0;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}
.service-features li::before{content:"✓";color:var(--g);font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0}
.service-btn{
  display:block;text-align:center;
  background:var(--dark);color:white;
  padding:12px;border-radius:10px;
  text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;font-size:0.9rem;
  transition:background 0.2s;
}
.service-btn:hover{background:var(--g)}
.service-card.featured .service-btn{background:var(--g)}
.service-card.featured .service-btn:hover{background:var(--g2)}

/* DISCOUNT SECTION */
.discount-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:1rem}
.discount-card{
  background:var(--dark);color:white;
  border-radius:16px;padding:1.5rem;text-align:center;
}
.discount-pct{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:3rem;font-weight:900;color:var(--g)}
.discount-card h4{font-size:0.9rem;font-weight:600;margin:0.5rem 0;color:white}
.discount-card p{font-size:0.8rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5)}
.promo-codes{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:1rem;margin-top:2rem}
.promo-code{
  background:white;border:2px dashed var(--g);
  border-radius:12px;padding:1rem 1.5rem;
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1rem;
}
.code{font-family:monospace;font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--g)}
.code-desc{font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--muted)}

/* CITIES */
.cities-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(160px,1fr));gap:1rem}
.city-card{
  border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;
  border:1px solid var(--border);
  transition:all 0.2s;cursor:pointer;text-decoration:none;color:inherit;
}
.city-card:hover{transform:translateY(-4px);box-shadow:var(--shadow)}
.city-img{height:120px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--g),var(--g2));display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:3rem}
.city-info{padding:1rem}
.city-info h4{font-weight:600;font-size:0.9rem;color:var(--dark)}
.city-info p{font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--muted);margin-top:2px}

/* PAYMENT */
.payment-section{background:var(--dark);padding:5rem 4rem;color:white}
.payment-inner{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto}
.payment-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(260px,1fr));gap:1.5rem;margin-top:3rem}
.payment-card{
  background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  border-radius:16px;padding:1.8rem;
}
.payment-card h3{font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;color:white;margin-bottom:0.5rem}
.payment-card p{font-size:0.875rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);margin-bottom:1rem}
.payment-detail{font-family:monospace;font-size:0.85rem;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);padding:10px 14px;border-radius:8px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);word-break:break-all}
.qr-box{text-align:center;margin-top:1rem}
.qr-box img{width:140px;border-radius:12px;background:white;padding:8px}

/* CONSULTANT */
.consultant-section{
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--g),var(--g2));
  padding:5rem 4rem;color:white;
}
.consultant-inner{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;display:grid;grid-template-columns:auto 1fr;gap:3rem;align-items:center}
.consultant-photo img{
  width:200px;height:200px;
  border-radius:50%;object-fit:cover;object-position:top;
  border:4px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
}
.consultant-info h2{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem}
.consultant-info .title{opacity:0.8;margin-bottom:1.5rem}
.consultant-info p{opacity:0.9;margin-bottom:2rem;max-width:500px;line-height:1.7}
.consult-btns{display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap}
.btn-white{
  background:white;color:var(--g);
  padding:12px 24px;border-radius:10px;
  text-decoration:none;font-weight:700;font-size:0.9rem;
  transition:all 0.2s;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;
}
.btn-white:hover{background:var(--bg)}
.btn-outline-white{
  background:transparent;color:white;
  padding:12px 24px;border-radius:10px;
  text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;font-size:0.9rem;
  border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
  transition:all 0.2s;
}
.btn-outline-white:hover{border-color:white}

/* RESOURCES */
.resources-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(260px,1fr));gap:1rem}
.resource-card{
  background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius:12px;padding:1.2rem;
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1rem;
  text-decoration:none;color:inherit;
  transition:all 0.2s;
}
.resource-card:hover{border-color:var(--g);box-shadow:var(--shadow)}
.resource-icon{font-size:1.5rem;flex-shrink:0}
.resource-card h4{font-size:0.875rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--dark)}
.resource-card p{font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--muted)}
.resource-arrow{margin-left:auto;color:var(--g);font-size:1.2rem;flex-shrink:0}

/* FOOTER */
footer{background:#0a0f0b;padding:3rem 4rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);text-align:center}
footer .footer-logo{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:1.5rem;color:white;margin-bottom:1rem}
footer p{font-size:0.85rem}
footer a{color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);text-decoration:none}
footer a:hover{color:white}

/* MOBILE */
@media(max-width:768px){
  nav{padding:0 1rem}
  .nav-links{display:none}
  .hero{grid-template-columns:1fr;padding:2rem 1.5rem;min-height:auto}
  .hero-image{order:-1}
  .hero-image img{height:280px}
  .hero-badge{bottom:-10px;left:10px}
  .stats-bar{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);padding:2rem 1.5rem}
  .section,.section-full{padding:3rem 1.5rem}
  .consultant-inner{grid-template-columns:1fr;text-align:center}
  .consultant-photo img{width:140px;height:140px}
  .consult-btns{justify-content:center}
  .payment-section{padding:3rem 1.5rem}
  .consultant-section{padding:3rem 1.5rem}
}
</style>
</head>
<body id="page" lang="en">

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <a class="logo" href="#">Study<em>Gate</em>Italy 🇮🇹</a>
  <div class="nav-right">
    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="#guides"><span class="en">Guides</span><span class="ar">الأدلة</span></a></li>
      <li><a href="#steps"><span class="en">How to Apply</span><span class="ar">كيفاش تسجل</span></a></li>
      <li><a href="#services"><span class="en">Services</span><span class="ar">الخدمات</span></a></li>
      <li><a href="#cities"><span class="en">Cities</span><span class="ar">المدن</span></a></li>
      <li><a href="#resources"><span class="en">Resources</span><span class="ar">الروابط</span></a></li>
    </ul>
    <button class="lang-toggle" onclick="toggleLang()">عربي / EN</button>
    <a href="#consult" class="cta-nav"><span class="en">Book Consultation</span><span class="ar">احجز استشارة</span></a>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-text">
    <p class="eyebrow en">For students from Algeria, Morocco, Tunisia & beyond</p>
    <p class="eyebrow ar">للطلاب من الجزائر، المغرب، تونس وأكثر</p>
    <h1 class="en">Your Gateway to <span>Studying in Italy</span> 🇮🇹</h1>
    <h1 class="ar">بوابتك للدراسة <span>في إيطاليا</span> 🇮🇹</h1>
    <p class="en">Everything you need — from Universitaly application to your first day in Italy. Real guides, real links, real help.</p>
    <p class="ar">كل شي تحتاجه — من التسجيل في Universitaly لأول يوم في إيطاليا. أدلة حقيقية، روابط حقيقية، مساعدة حقيقية.</p>
    <div class="hero-btns">
      <a href="#steps" class="btn-primary"><span class="en">Start Your Journey →</span><span class="ar">ابدا رحلتك ←</span></a>
      <a href="#services" class="btn-secondary"><span class="en">Our Services</span><span class="ar">خدماتنا</span></a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-image">
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1523906834658-6e24ef2386f9?w=800&q=80" alt="Italy Study">
    <div class="hero-badge">
      <div class="number">90+</div>
      <div class="label en">Italian Universities</div>
      <div class="label ar">جامعة إيطالية</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- STATS BAR -->
<div class="stats-bar">
  <div class="stat"><div class="n">50K+</div><div class="l en">International Students</div><div class="l ar">طالب دولي</div></div>
  <div class="stat"><div class="n">€0</div><div class="l en">Public Tuition</div><div class="l ar">تعليم مجاني</div></div>
  <div class="stat"><div class="n">5K€+</div><div class="l en">DSU Scholarship/year</div><div class="l ar">منحة DSU/سنة</div></div>
  <div class="stat"><div class="n">800+</div><div class="l en">Years of Academia</div><div class="l ar">سنة أكاديمية</div></div>
</div>

<!-- GUIDES -->
<div class="section" id="guides">
  <p class="eyebrow en">Complete Guides</p>
  <p class="eyebrow ar">أدلة كاملة</p>
  <h2 class="section-title en">Everything You Need to Know</h2>
  <h2 class="section-title ar">كل شي تحتاج تعرفه</h2>
  <p class="section-sub en">Step-by-step guides for every part of your Italian study journey</p>
  <p class="section-sub ar">أدلة خطوة بخطوة لكل مرحلة في رحلتك الدراسية في إيطاليا</p>
  <div class="guides-grid">
    <a href="https://www.universitaly.it" target="_blank" class="guide-card">
      <div class="guide-icon">🎓</div>
      <h3 class="en">Universitaly Registration</h3>
      <h3 class="ar">التسجيل في Universitaly</h3>
      <p class="en">Complete step-by-step guide — account creation, document upload, validation tracking and what to do if blocked.</p>
      <p class="ar">دليل كامل — إنشاء الحساب، رفع الوثائق، متابعة التحقق وماذا تفعل إذا تم حظر ملفك.</p>
      <span class="guide-tag en">Essential First Step</span>
      <span class="guide-tag ar">أول خطوة أساسية</span>
    </a>
    <a href="#" class="guide-card">
      <div class="guide-icon">🛂</div>
      <h3 class="en">Student Visa Type D — Full Dossier</h3>
      <h3 class="ar">فيزا الطالب النوع D — الدوسيي الكامل</h3>
      <p class="en">Exact list of required documents, embassy links for Algeria/Morocco/Tunisia/Uzbekistan, certified translator contacts.</p>
      <p class="ar">القائمة الدقيقة للوثائق المطلوبة، روابط السفارات للجزائر/المغرب/تونس/أوزبكستان، جهات المترجمين المعتمدين.</p>
      <span class="guide-tag en">Critical Document</span>
      <span class="guide-tag ar">وثيقة أساسية</span>
    </a>
    <a href="#" class="guide-card">
      <div class="guide-icon">🏠</div>
      <h3 class="en">Finding Housing in Italy</h3>
      <h3 class="ar">إيجاد السكن في إيطاليا</h3>
      <p class="en">Best websites: Idealista, Immobiliare, Uniplaces. Ready-to-send message templates in Italian. How to avoid scams.</p>
      <p class="ar">أفضل المواقع: Idealista، Immobiliare، Uniplaces. قوالب رسائل جاهزة بالإيطالية. كيفاش تتجنب النصب.</p>
      <span class="guide-tag en">Save Money</span>
      <span class="guide-tag ar">وفر المال</span>
    </a>
    <a href="#" class="guide-card">
      <div class="guide-icon">💰</div>
      <h3 class="en">DSU / ISEE Scholarship</h3>
      <h3 class="ar">منحة DSU / ISEE</h3>
      <p class="en">Free housing + meals + up to 5,000€/year cash. How to apply, deadlines per city, ISEE calculation for foreign students.</p>
      <p class="ar">سكن مجاني + وجبات + حتى 5,000€/سنة كاش. كيفاش تقدم، المواعيد لكل مدينة، حساب ISEE للطلاب الأجانب.</p>
      <span class="guide-tag en">Free Money!</span>
      <span class="guide-tag ar">مال مجاني!</span>
    </a>
    <a href="#" class="guide-card">
      <div class="guide-icon">📄</div>
      <h3 class="en">First 30 Days in Italy</h3>
      <h3 class="ar">أول 30 يوم في إيطاليا</h3>
      <p class="en">Codice Fiscale → Permesso di Soggiorno (within 8 days!) → Tessera Sanitaria → Bank account. Day-by-day checklist.</p>
      <p class="ar">Codice Fiscale ← Permesso di Soggiorno (خلال 8 أيام!) ← Tessera Sanitaria ← الحساب البنكي. قائمة تحقق يوم بيوم.</p>
      <span class="guide-tag en">Urgent — Do First</span>
      <span class="guide-tag ar">عاجل — افعل أولاً</span>
    </a>
    <a href="#" class="guide-card">
      <div class="guide-icon">💼</div>
      <h3 class="en">Working While Studying</h3>
      <h3 class="ar">العمل أثناء الدراسة</h3>
      <p class="en">You can work 20 hours/week as a foreign student. Best job platforms: Indeed.it, InfoJobs, LinkedIn. Italian CV template included.</p>
      <p class="ar">تقدر تشتغل 20 ساعة/أسبوع كطالب أجنبي. أفضل منصات العمل: Indeed.it، InfoJobs، LinkedIn. قالب CV إيطالي متضمن.</p>
      <span class="guide-tag en">Earn Extra Income</span>
      <span class="guide-tag ar">اكسب دخلاً إضافياً</span>
    </a>
  </div>
